'''''African Jim''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''Jim Aza i Jo'burg''''', ni filime yo muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo yasohotse muri 1949<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/jim-comes-to-joburg/</ref>, iyobowe na Donald Swanson kandi yakozwe na Eric Rutherford. Irimo Daniel Adnewmah, Dolly Rathebe, Inkspots nyafurika, Sam Maile, na Dan Twala. <ref>[http://www.villonfilms.ca/african-jim/ Peter Davis, "African Jim", 12 November 2012]. Villon Films.</ref> Birazwi cyane nka republika ya Afrika yepfo film ya mbere yuburebure bwa [[Afurika|Afrika]]<ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/african-jim-jim-comes-to-joburg/oclc/66619727</ref>. 

== Tegura ibisobanuro ==
Jim yavuye mu gace k'imiryango gushaka umutungo we i Johannesburg<ref>https://www.3continents.com/en/film/african-jim/</ref>. Akimara kuhagera, abambari batatu baramukubita. Iyo agaruye ubwenge, umuzamu w'ijoro wa gicuti amwitaho<ref>https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.1080/13696810903488595</ref>. Abifashijwemo n'umuzamu, Jim abona akazi muri club ya nijoro nk'umukozi<ref>https://www.nypl.org/events/programs/2010/02/27/south-african-musical-film-%E2%80%94-african-jim-1949-zonk-1950</ref>. Yahawe amahirwe yo kuririmbira kuri stage hamwe numurimbyikazi  wikipe, Dolly<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/239480-african-jim</ref>. Mbere yuko atangira bwa mbere, amenya abambari bamusahuye kandi yumva ko bategura ubujura<ref>http://www.colonialfilm.org.uk/node/1139</ref>. Jim agomba guhitamo uburyo bwo guhagarika icyaha kandi akiri mugihe cyo gukora<ref>https://www.cinemagia.ro/filme/african-jim-50406/</ref>.  

